34:47.186 --> 34:49.352
Had to say good-bye.

34:55.326 --> 34:57.360
(Polisi)
In the life,

34:57.362 --> 34:59.463
you justify your actions

34:59.465 --> 35:02.365
and you figure a way out
to make yourself believe

35:02.367 --> 35:05.402
that it's okay
to do illegal things,

35:05.404 --> 35:08.205
immoral things,
commit acts of violence.

35:11.309 --> 35:13.276
You can't have any regrets.

35:16.247 --> 35:19.549
(narrator)
On June 20th, 1947,

35:19.551 --> 35:23.854
Bugsy Siegel is shot
nine times in Beverly Hills.

35:23.856 --> 35:26.189
Siegel becomes

35:26.191 --> 35:28.325
the first of Luciano's
original crew

35:28.327 --> 35:30.393
to be killed.

35:33.297 --> 35:35.165
The death of
Bugsy Siegel still--

35:35.167 --> 35:36.500
it's like the death
of John F. Kennedy.

35:36.502 --> 35:37.868
It's a big mystery.

35:37.870 --> 35:40.504
He lost a lot of
the mob's money.

35:40.506 --> 35:43.540
And he had done something
that people got killed for

35:43.542 --> 35:45.275
doing with the mob.

35:45.277 --> 35:47.511
And the people most often
killed by the mob

35:47.513 --> 35:50.514
are other mobsters, so it
seems to fit that pattern.

35:52.783 --> 35:55.152
(Green)
Exactly what was decided

35:55.154 --> 35:57.287
is not entirely known.

35:57.289 --> 35:59.523
As for who did it,
there have been stories

35:59.525 --> 36:01.691
that it was this hit man
or that hit man.

36:01.693 --> 36:03.527
That it was because
of the skimming,

36:03.529 --> 36:05.929
that it was due to the Flamingo
not making profits.

36:05.931 --> 36:09.199
There's even a theory that
because he and Virginia Hill

36:09.201 --> 36:11.735
had a very difficult
relationship,

36:11.737 --> 36:13.937
that her brother
was avenging that,

36:13.939 --> 36:16.306
and it had nothing to do
with the mob.

36:16.308 --> 36:17.874
What happened?

36:17.876 --> 36:19.876
Well, according to the Beverly
Hills Police Department,

36:19.878 --> 36:22.179
it is still an open case.

36:23.548 --> 36:26.316
(narrator)
20 minutes after his murder,

36:26.318 --> 36:28.718
Meyer Lansky's men

36:28.720 --> 36:31.621
take control of
the Flamingo.

